I18N_ABOUT_PAGE_ABOUT_TAB_PARAGRAPH_1: Tuɣdaḍt n Oppia d amuddu n ufus i yal yiwen ad yissin ayen yebɣa s wudem amellil d zhu.
I18N_ABOUT_PAGE_ABOUT_TAB_PARAGRAPH_2: S tmerna n tagrumma n timsirin tilelliyin n tɣara meqqren, i nezmer ad d-nessebgen, s tallelt n imsegmiyen n umaḍal, Oppia tettnadi ad d-mudd i yinelmaden assegmi n tɣara — di yal amdiq anida llan akked tiɣbula tinsayanin anida zemren ad kecmen.
I18N_ABOUT_PAGE_ABOUT_TAB_PARAGRAPH_3: Akka tura, imsegmiyen rnan ugar n <[numberOfExplorations]> n timsirin, imumi nessawal isnirmen. Timsirin ttwaseqdacent sɣur <[numberofStudentsServed]> n inelmaden deg umaḍal.
I18N_ABOUT_PAGE_ABOUT_TAB_PARAGRAPH_4: Isnirmen ttmuddun afus i yinelmaden ad lemden s wudem n zhu d usnulfu, s useqdec n tvidyutin, tugniwinakked isteqsiyen yeldin. Imiinelmaden ɣur-sen yal tikelt tuccḍiwin di tiktiwin, Oppia tettmuddu-d daɣen i yimsegmiyen  tagnitt akken ad seɣtin srid deg isnirmen, s umuddu n tiktiwin ibanen i ddeqs n inelmaden deg iwen n wakud.
I18N_ABOUT_PAGE_ABOUT_TAB_PARAGRAPH_5: Ma d anelmad i telliḍ udiɣ tebɣiḍ ad tlemdeḍ s Oppia, tzemreḍ ad tegreḍ aḍaṛ deg ulmad s usnirem deg timsirin-nneɣ.
I18N_ABOUT_PAGE_ABOUT_TAB_PARAGRAPH_6: Ma kečč d aselmad iḥemmlen aselmed n inelmaden n umaḍal meṛṛa, tzemreḍ ad tsutreḍ ad tedduḍ ar wahil-nneɣ Selmed s Oppia, yettheggin timsirin ɣef isental i ttafen inelmaden weɛrit.
I18N_ABOUT_PAGE_ABOUT_TAB_PARAGRAPH_7: S uselmed s Oppia, ad tizmireḍ ad tesnerniḍ tiwezza-ik n teywalt d uḥemmel n wiyaḍ s umuddu n ufus deg usnerni n usegmi n umaḍal meṛṛa. Neɣ, ma yella ur theggad ara iman-ik i uselmed, tzemred ad tebḍuḍ tikti-ik ɣef timsirin akken ad d-muddeḍ ayen yufraren i yinelmaden nniḍen.
I18N_ABOUT_PAGE_ABOUT_TAB_PARAGRAPH_8: Telliḍ ama d aselmad K-12, anelmad s ugerdas neɣ amdan iḥemmlen asentel ibanen, udiɣ tebɣiḍ ad tebḍuḍ tamusni-ik, Oppia yeqqar-ak anṣuf yis-k. Ddu ar uẓeṭṭa sakin bdu asnirem yid-neɣ.
I18N_ABOUT_PAGE_CREDITS_TAB_TEXT: Iwiziwen n Oppia usan-d seg umaḍal meṛṛa —ddeqs seg-neɣ d inelmaden akked iselmaden imaynuten. Nebɣa ad nesnemmer iwiziwen-agi i d-imudden afus di bennu n usmel-agi. Ma tebɣiḍ ad tmuddeḍ afus , hata wamek ara tettekkiḍ!

I18N_ABOUT_PAGE_FOUNDATION_TAB_PARAGRAPH: Asmel Web n Oppia d tenglat-is aɣbalu terfed-itent Tasbadeddit Oppia, tuddsa ur yettxelliṣen ara tabzert 501(c)(3), yettwaskelsen di tmurt n Kalifurnya di Marikan.
Tasbeddit tettkel ɣe umwiwen n iwiziwen d wid yettmuddun tawsa seg umaḍal meṛṛa akken ad tessiweḍ tuɣdaḍt-is n uselmed swudem fessusen, s wudem ara d-yawin tamusni s zreb.
Ma tebɣiḍ ad tedduḍ ar twinas n imdanen nniden i yettmuddun afus, wali ugar di amuddu n yidrimen i Oppia Foundation neɣ ttekki s tarrayin nniḍen.
Inemhalen n tsebeddit d Amit Deutsch, Jacob Davis, akked Sean Lip. ilugan d tiktiwin n tesbeddit llan i tquri. Ma tebɣiḍ ad tneremseḍ tasbeddit, azen imayl ar: admin@oppia.org.

Akk agbur di timsirin n Oppia yella ddaw n turagt CC-BY-SA 4.0 s smeḥ n hettem n tikci (ladɣa, tigezmiyin 3(a)(1) akked 3(a)(2)). Ma yella tulseḍ aseqdec n ugbur seg usmel-agi, seddu, ma ulac aɣilif, aseɣwen ar usebter n temsirt, acu kan mačči d ayen ilaqen.
Aseɣzan iselkamen Oppia d aɣbalu yeldin, akked tangalt-is yeffeɣ-d ddaw n turagt Apache 2.0.

I18N_SPLASH_FIRST_EXPLORATION_DESCRIPTIO: Timsirin n Oppia, yettawsnen daɣen s yisem n isniram, ttmuddun-d tirmitin timyigawanin ifazen ugar n tvidyutin neɣ iḍrisen, akken ad mudden tallelt i yiseqdacen ad issinen yis-n.
I18N_SPLASH_JAVASCRIPT_ERROR_DESCRIPTION: Oppia d asmel ilelli n uɣbalu yeldin n irmuden imyigawnanen ittusemman 'isniram'. Acu kan, Oppia yesra JavaScript ad yettwarmed ɣef iminig-ik web akken ad yeddu akken iwata, ihi ɣef iminig-ik yensa. Ma tesriḍ tallelt akken ad tremdeḍ JavaScript, sit dagi.
I18N_SPLASH_SECOND_EXPLORATION_DESCRIPTI: Isniram fessus-it i tmerna. Ttawin abrid n tiktiwin i d-ttmuddun yimdanen u teddun akken tella termit n inelmaden-ik deg umaḍal.
I18N_SPLASH_SUBTITLE: Oppia yessifses timerna n timsirin timyigawanin i yesselmaden, i yelledayen allen.
I18N_SPLASH_THIRD_EXPLORATION_DESCRIPTIO: Oppia ad k-yeǧǧ ad ternuḍ udiɣ ad tebḍuḍ isniram n ddeqs n isental, ala axemmem-ik kan ara yilin d talast.
I18N_TEACH_PAGE_COMMUNITY_GUIDELINES_GUI: Yal yiwen ansuf yis-s akken ad yeɛreḍ udiɣ ad d-imudd tikti-s ɣef isniram i d-yeffɣen. S wafus-nwen meṛṛa, Ad nizmir ad nesnerni s war aneḥbus, timsirin ɣef usmel sakin ad tent-nerr lhan ugar akken nezmer.
Seqdec tamuɣli yelhan ticki tessuffuɣeḍ-d isniram. Isniram yessefk ad sɛun azal n usegmi ibanen udiq ur yessefk ara ad yegber adellel, ispamen, aḥwaṣ neɣ asexṣer.

Ili-k d aɣerman yelhan. Timerna n ddeqs n imiḍanen, aseqdec s waṭas n unagraw n tiktiwin, aseqdec n yisniram akken ad tkelxeḍ iseqdacen, neɣ yal tikli am tigi ur tettwaqbal ara dagi udiɣ ad yeglu s useḥbes n umiḍan-ik
I18N_TEACH_PAGE_COMMUNITY_GUIDELINES_TEX: Ma tebɣiḍ asegzi ɣef tinaḍin-agi, suter deg unmager-nneɣ.
I18N_TEACH_PAGE_HEADING: Mudd afus i yinelmaden n umaḍal
I18N_TEACH_PAGE_PUBLICATION_INSTRUCTIONS: Selmed taɣawsa yelhan — Mudd-d talɣut tamaynut i wid yimsefliden isaḍasen — ur sekyad ara kan tamusni i ẓran yakan. Daɣen, ma tebɣiḍ ad teslemdeḍ asentel anida yella yakan usnirem, xemmem ad ternuḍ awennit ɣef usnirem amiran, akken ad tmuddeḍ afus deg usnerni-is — akka ifessus!

Aselmed mačči d aḥekku — Ma tferneḍ isental, ɛreḍ ad tferneḍ, ad tawdiḍ tikti iweɛren yesɛan ddeqs n inumak neɣ leqqayet nezzeh, neɣ tagrumma n isentall yemcubaken aṭas. Yezmer daɣen yelha limer ad tesɛuḍ tikti n unerni neɣ acqirreq, akken aselmad ad yesɛu tagnitt ad yesnes tikti i yelmed yakan ɣef yiwet n lḥala tamaynut.

Mudd tikti ibennun — Ur qqar ara kan i unelmad d akken yufa-tt-id neɣ yeɣleḍ. Segzi-yas amek ara yexemmem, neɣ ddu s telqayt akken ad tɛerḍeḍ ad gzun tuccḍiwin. Seqdec ismektiyen neɣ mudd iwellihen i yisteqsiyen yeldin, udiɣ mudd i yinelmaden tiktiwin timaynutin ilaqen.
Ales taɣuri — Ḍmen d akken asnirem-ik yura akken iwata, fessus i tɣuri. Yessefk ad yilis war tuccḍiqin n tira neɣ ibugen, acku ad yesruḥ taflest deg inelmaden.

Mudd-itt-id s tseddi — Iswi n uselmed ad yettwabgen i yinelmaden yettnadin isniram, udiɣ yessefk ad d-imudd udem n ugbur n usnirem-ik. Asnirem yessefk ad d-imudd akk agbur n umiru yellan deg iswi n uselmed akked usnirem iman-is.

Qqim d imseknu! — Isniram ifazen ḥekkun-d taqsiḍt, ttarand- tikti ilaqen. Ttmuddun i yinelmaden tignatin n uxemmem ɣef imegziyen, aɛraḍ n timusniwin timaynutin, d urmas n tiktiwin ilaqen ɣef umahil-nsen.
Ticki yeffeɣ-d usnirem, ad k-ittunefk, udiɣ ad yili yewjed i yal yiwen yebɣan ad yelmed seg-s akken ad d-yesnulfu tarmit ifazen i yinelmaden, hatent-a kra  n tixbula i nufa lhant!
Ugar n tallelt ɣef tmerna n tikti yelhan akked isniram ifazen, wali asebter-nneɣ di Design Tips.
I18N_TEACH_PAGE_PUBLICATION_POLICY_PARAG: Yal ameskar n usnirem uslig ad yizmir ad tt-id-yessuffeɣ melmi yebɣa. Acu kan, isniram n yir taɣara, inedbalen zemren ad ten-tḥebsen, sakin ad d-mudden ayen ilaqen akken ad nernint.

Isniram ttwafeṣlen akken ad ttnernin, tid ur nettwabeddel ara ddeqs nwakud zmrent ad ttwaḥesbent d "tigujilin". Ihi, zemrent ad beddlent bab akken ad uɣalent n tmezdagnut Oppia (akken i ɣ-d-iwelleh unedbal), akken ad tizmir ad tennerni.
